        <item>
            <title>风雨中拍摄痛苦发飙戏</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_486611540100m6gd.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
来无锡这么多天一直艳阳高照，昨夜拍夜戏竟然风雨交加，可怜我穿得单薄的戏服，但是现在工作气氛很好，让我心里感到温暖。</P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h951114b35e42" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="439" SRC="http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h951114b35e42&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br /></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
哈哈~蓝志伟导演这张很可爱吧~大家知道昨晚有多冷吧？</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h951196164025" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="388" SRC="http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h951196164025&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br /></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
我和三浦贵大的第一场戏。我告诉他我爸妈是他爸妈的粉丝。三浦是一个非常内向慢热的男生，很有礼貌很谦逊，很开心可以认识并合作，他告诉我我名字的“爽”日语中的发音是“白天鹅”的意思，好美的名字哦~说得我心里美美的~</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h95118bfcda2d" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h95118bfcda2d&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
以为这次会很淑女，实际上是穿着淑女装的野蛮淘气女生。<br />
<br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h9511391baa32" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h9511391baa32&amp;690" />
</A></P>
<p><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h95113dcecfc4" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h95113dcecfc4&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h754e9bc8f80a" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="470" SRC="http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h754e9bc8f80a&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br />
<br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h9511424746a4" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h9511424746a4&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
气的把鞋都扔了，三浦饰演暗恋我的天明把它捡回来~</P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h754e977343ba" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h754e977343ba&amp;690" WIDTH="488" /></A><br />
<br /></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
这场戏是接和王子饰演的“清风”吵架后的，看我发疯的样子就知道我被气的有多严重~<br /></P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154hdd2b042563c3" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="448" SRC="http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154hdd2b042563c3&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A></P>
<p><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h9511aa952df1" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="388" SRC="http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h9511aa952df1&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br />
<br />
<br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h9511a5ca2d42" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h9511a5ca2d42&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
我觉得整张像尊雕塑~下半身国的特贵气吧嘿嘿~</P>
<p><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h9511b0b8f4d6" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="388" SRC="http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h9511b0b8f4d6&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br />
<br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154hdd2ae8ea08f9" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154hdd2ae8ea08f9&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
拍摄间隙还要织围脖~</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/48661154h951179fc75d1" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="690" SRC="http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/48661154h951179fc75d1&amp;690" WIDTH="388" /></A><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
之后会陆续拍摄《极速先锋》的工作照片，请关注~</P>]]></description>
